{"entries":[{"id":"tsk-gen-8-6","title":"Genesis 8:6","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":8,"verseStart":6,"chapterEnd":8,"verseEnd":6},"content":"<p>Ex 20:12; Le 19:32; Ro 13:7; Ga 6:1; 1Ti 5:1,17,19; 1Pe 2:17; 4:8</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-8-11","title":"Genesis 8:11","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":8,"verseStart":11,"chapterEnd":8,"verseEnd":11},"content":"<p>A.M. 2006. B.C. 1998. nine. 5:5,20,27,32; 11:11-25; Ps 90:10</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-8-16","title":"Genesis 8:16","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":8,"verseStart":16,"chapterEnd":8,"verseEnd":16},"content":"<p>A.M. 1757. B.C. 2247. isles. 25; Ps 72:10; Isa 24:15; 40:15; 41:5; 42:4,10; 49:1; 51:5; 59:18 Isa 60:9; Jer 2:10; 25:22; Zep 2:11 after his. 20; 11:1-9</p>"},{"id":"tsk-gen-8-21","title":"Genesis 8:21","author":"R. A. Torrey (editor)","reference":{"book":"GEN","chapterStart":8,"verseStart":21,"chapterEnd":8,"verseEnd":21},"content":"<p>A.M. 1700. B.C. 2304. went forth Asshur. or, he went outinto Assyria. Mic 5:6 Asshur. Nu 24:22,24; Ezr 4:2; Ps 83:8; Eze 27:23; 32:22; Ho 14:3 Nineveh. 2Ki 19:36; Isa 37:37; Jon 1:2; 3:1-10; Na 1:1; 2:8; 3:7; Zep 2:13 the city of. or, the streets of the city.</p>"}]}